{
  "version": 1,
  "course": {
    "id": "nce1-063-064-thank-you-doctor",
    "title": "Lesson 63: Thank you, doctor.",
    "audioFilename": "063&064－Thank You, Doctor..mp3",
    "duration": 103.131,
    "language": "en"
  },
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "start": 0.46,
      "end": 2.16,
      "text": "Lesson 63.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "第63课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "start": 3.38,
      "end": 4.7,
      "text": "Thank You, Doctor.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "谢谢您，医生。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "start": 6.42,
      "end": 11.04,
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "start": 12.64,
      "end": 15.16,
      "text": "Who else is in bed today?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "今天还有谁卧床了？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "start": 16.28,
      "end": 16.84,
      "text": "Why?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "为什么？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "start": 19.3,
      "end": 20.76,
      "text": "How's Jimmy today?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "吉米今天怎么样？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "start": 21.66,
      "end": 22,
      "text": "He's better.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他好些了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "start": 22.7,
      "end": 27.46,
      "text": "Thank you, Doctor. Can I see him, please, Mrs. Williams?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "谢谢您，医生。我可以看看他吗，威廉斯太太？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "start": 29.06,
      "end": 30.54,
      "text": "Certainly, Doctor.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "当然可以，医生。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "start": 31.4,
      "end": 32.46,
      "text": "Come upstairs.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "请上楼。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "start": 34.1,
      "end": 36.12,
      "text": "You look very well, Jimmy.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你看起来很好，吉米。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "start": 37.02,
      "end": 41.4,
      "text": "You are better now, but you mustn't get up yet.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你现在好多了，但还不能起床。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "start": 42.38,
      "end": 46.6,
      "text": "You must stay in bed for another two days.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你必须再卧床两天。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "start": 48.24,
      "end": 51.74,
      "text": "The boy mustn't go to school yet, Mrs.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这个孩子还不能去上学，威廉斯"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "start": 51.92,
      "end": 55.88,
      "text": "Williams, and he mustn't eat rich food.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "太太，而且他不能吃油腻的食物。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "start": 57.16,
      "end": 61.06,
      "text": "Does he have a temperature, Doctor?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他发烧吗，医生？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "start": 62.08,
      "end": 63.64,
      "text": "No, he doesn't.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "不发烧。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "start": 64.24,
      "end": 66.22,
      "text": "Must he stay in bed?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他必须卧床吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "start": 66.94,
      "end": 71.8,
      "text": "Yes, he must remain in bed for another two days.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "是的，他必须再卧床两天。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "start": 72.78,
      "end": 77.16,
      "text": "He can get up for about two hours each day.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他每天可以起床两小时左右。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "start": 77.92,
      "end": 81.04,
      "text": "But you must keep the room warm.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "但您必须保持房间温暖。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "start": 83.53,
      "end": 84.45,
      "text": "Where's Mr. Williams",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "威廉斯先生在哪里"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s023",
      "start": 85.01,
      "end": 86.31,
      "text": "this evening?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "今晚在哪里？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s024",
      "start": 87.11,
      "end": 89.51,
      "text": "He's in bed, Doctor.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他躺在床上，医生。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s025",
      "start": 90.53,
      "end": 92.29,
      "text": "Can you see him, please?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "您能看看他吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s026",
      "start": 93.29,
      "end": 96.05,
      "text": "He has a bad cold, too.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他也得了重感冒。"
      }
    }
  ]
}
